bio: <p>Anton Koovit was born in Tallinn, Estonia, in 1981. He studied graphic \
  design in Estonian Academy of Arts, ESAG Paris and in Gerrit Rietveld \
  Academy in Amsterdam, Holland. After completing graphic design studies in \
  2005 he continued to specialize in Type Design on a postgraduate course Type \
  and Media (KABK) in The Hague, Holland. Since completing studies in 2006 \
  Anton set up his own company Khork OÃœ and is working on wide range of \
  projects starting from exhibition design to designing logos, posters and \
  typefaces.</p>\
  <p>In 2007 he moved to Berlin, Germany. Besides typographic work he is \
  teaching typography and giving type design workshops. Typefaces by Anton \
  Koovit: Adam BP, Aleksei, GQ Slab, U8, Arvo.</p>
